Every 1-2 years i travel{{item:3009}}  from Australia{{champion:58}}  back to United Kingdom{{champion:51}}   to visit family for a month during this time{{item:3157}}  there is alot of free time where family and friends are busy so i normally play games and my favorite game to kill time is LoL{{summoner:3}} .

With that being said every time i visit the UK{{champion:51}}  for 4 weeks i have to pay a stupid amount of $50{{item:3400}}  to be able to transfer{{summoner:12}}  my account to EU and back to OCE when i return......

This is such a waste of money for me as im not where for alot of time at all and its just so expensive{{item:3400}}  to move an account over WHY is there not a one time payment to buy certain regions for moving freely or at least allow us to use Blue Essence FFS.

And yes i know your all gonna say just make another account to play on in the UK{{champion:51}}  but thats what sucks so much as i have spent so much money{{item:2319}}  on skins and play time to max my account........

RIP MY WALLET{{summoner:11}} 

anyone else have the same issue?{{summoner:14}}
